*ruby-libglade-0.29 (06 Jul 2002)

	06 Jul 2002: Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> ruby-libglade-0.29.ebuild:

	Version 0.29 is NEWER than 1.2 because it changed maintainership and was
	rolled into the ruby-gnome package.  ruby-libglade-1.2 should never have
	been put into Gentoo, though that wasn't obvious from the version numbers.
	Added SLOT and LICENSE.

*ruby-libglade-1.2 (27 May 2002)

	27 May 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> ruby-libglade-1.2.ebuild
	files/digest-ruby-libglade-1.2 :

	ekarttun@cs.helsinki.fi (Einar Karttunen) submitted this much needed
	update in bug #1258.  This version of the package is not a ruby-gnome
	package, but actually a ruby-libglade package.
